Task A

# Task: Calculate average tortilla prices for 2007 and 2024

# Filter data for the year 2007
avg_price_2007 <- tortilla_data %>%
  filter(year == 2007) %>%
  summarise(avg_price = mean(price, na.rm = TRUE))

# Filter data for the year 2024
avg_price_2024 <- tortilla_data %>%
  filter(year == 2024) %>%
  summarise(avg_price = mean(price, na.rm = TRUE))

# Display results
avg_price_2007
# A tibble: 1 Ã 1
  avg_price
      <dbl>
1      7.68
avg_price_2024
# A tibble: 1 Ã 1
  avg_price
      <dbl>
1      20.5

Task b

percent_change <- (avg_price_2024$avg_price - avg_price_2007$avg_price) / avg_price_2007$avg_price * 100

percent_change
[1] 166.4113

Task c

yearly_avg_prices <- tortilla_data %>%
  group_by(year) %>%
  summarise(avg_price = mean(price, na.rm = TRUE))

ggplot(yearly_avg_prices, aes(x = year, y = avg_price)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(
    title = "Average Tortilla Prices in Border States (2007â2024)",
    x = "Year",
    y = "Average Price (MXN)"
  )

Task d

data_2016 <- tortilla_data %>%
  filter(year == 2016)

summary_stats <- data_2016 %>%
  group_by(state) %>%
  summarise(
    avg_price = mean(price, na.rm = TRUE),
    median_price = median(price, na.rm = TRUE),
    sd_price = sd(price, na.rm = TRUE)
  )


summary_stats
